WEBVTT

00:02.135 --> 00:03.432
<i>Previously on</i> Vampire Diaries:

00:03.602 --> 00:06.003
- You must be Elena.
- How do we look exactly alike?

00:06.206 --> 00:08.674
You're a Petrova doppelganger.
The key to the curse.

00:08.842 --> 00:11.333
Klaus is a vampire
born from a werewolf bloodline.

00:11.511 --> 00:13.809
The curse kept his werewolf
from manifesting.

00:13.980 --> 00:17.279
He'll be vulnerable during the
transformation, when Bonnie comes in.

00:17.450 --> 00:19.782
If she can deliver him
to the brink of death, I'll finish the job.

00:19.953 --> 00:22.581
I had a family.
Klaus hunted them down one by one.

00:22.756 --> 00:25.623
He scattered them
where their bodies could not be found.

00:25.792 --> 00:29.091
I didn't bury them at sea.
Their bodies are safe.

00:29.262 --> 00:31.662
If you kill me, you'll never find them.

00:31.831 --> 00:33.093
No!

00:33.266 --> 00:35.496
Who's gonna save your life
while you're making decisions?

00:35.668 --> 00:37.795
- I don't want to be saved.
- There is a way.

00:37.971 --> 00:39.700
What are you...? Damon, no.

00:39.873 --> 00:40.931
I fed her my blood.

00:41.107 --> 00:43.302
She'll come back a vampire.
How could you?

00:43.476 --> 00:45.103
She'll never forgive you.

00:45.278 --> 00:48.179
- Tyler Lockwood bit me.
- A werewolf bite can kill a vampire.

00:50.000 --> 00:56.074
